articles.title: Australia’s PM slams vandalism of US consulate with pro-Palestine graffiti - Al Jazeera English
articles.description: Australia’s Anthony Albanese calls on protesters to ‘turn the heat down’ after US consulate has windows smashed.
articles.content:
Australian Prime Minister Anthony Albanese has condemned an incident in which the US consulate in Sydney was attacked with a sledgehammer and defaced with pro-Palestinian graffiti.
